th Memory Tricks | KanjiGami\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Master Japanese Kanji through memorable stories, memory tricks, interesting facts, example words, and JLPT-focused study guides.\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"KanjiGami\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Learn Japanese Kanji with Memory Tricks | KanjiGami\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Master Japanese Kanji through memorable stories, memory tricks, interesting facts, example words, and JLPT-focused study guides.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/icon.png\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-full flex flex-col\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\" hidden 2xl:block fixed left-20 top-[140px] z-40 \"><div class=\"w-[120px] h-[400px] border rounded-2xl bg-white shadow flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400 text-sm\">Advertisement</div></div><div class=\"flex-1 pb-20\"><header class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white border-b\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"h-16 md:h-20 flex items-center justify-between\"><div><div class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold\"><span class=\"text-black\">Kanji</span><span class=\"text-green-800\">Gami</span></div><div class=\"text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-500\">Remembering Kanji Made Easy.</div></div><nav class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-6 text-sm font-medium\"><a href=\"/\" class=\"hover:text-green-700\">🏠 Home</a><a href=\"/jlpt/n5\" class=\"hover:text-green-700\">📘 N5 Kanji</a><a href=\"/jlpt/n4\" class=\"hover:text-green-700\">📗 N4 Kanji</a><a href=\"/search\">🔍 Search</a></nav></div></div><div class=\"md:hidden border-t bg-slate-50\"><div class=\"flex justify-around py-2 text-xs font-medium\"><a href=\"/\">🏠 Home</a><a href=\"/jlpt/n5\">📘 N5 Kanji</a><a href=\"/jlpt/n4\">📗 N4 Kanji</a><a href=\"/search\">🔍 Search</a></div></div></header><section class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-6 md:py-10\"><div class=\"bg-white border rounded-3xl p-5 md:p-10\"><div class=\"text-center text-green-800 font-bold text-xl md:text-3xl mb-6 md:mb-10 tracking-wide\">KANJI OF THE DAY</div><div class=\"mb-5 md:mb-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"text-[80px] md:text-[120px] leading-none\">男</div><div class=\"text-sm md:text-lg text-gray-500 mt-1 text-center\">おとこ (otoko)</div></div><div class=\"flex-1 flex items-center\"><div class=\"text-xl md:text-3xl font-semibold break-words\">Man, Male</div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-4 md:p-6 mb-4\"><h2 class=\"text-green-800 font-bold text-lg md:text-xl mb-2\">Interesting Fact</h2><p class=\"text-sm md:text-lg leading-6 md:leading-8 text-gray-700\">Every winter, thousands of men take part in &quot;Hadaka Matsuri&quot;, Japan&#x27;s famous &quot;Naked Festival.&quot; Wearing little more than a traditional loincloth, they brave the cold and push through packed crowds to receive sacred objects believed to bring good fortune. The tradition grew from ancient purification rituals, where enduring hardship was seen as a way to drive away bad luck and begin the year renewed.</p></div><div class=\"bg-green-50 rounded-2xl p-4 md:p-6 mb-5\"><h2 class=\"text-green-800 font-bold text-lg md:text-xl mb-2\">Memory Trick</h2><p class=\"text-sm md:text-lg leading-6 md:leading-8 text-gray-700\">A rice field (田) doesn&#x27;t plow itself. It takes a man with strength (力) to work it. That&#x27;s why 田 + 力 = 男.</p></div><a class=\"inline-block bg-green-800 hover:bg-green-900 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-xl font-medium text-sm\" href=\"/kanji/kanji-man-male\">View Full Details →</a></div></section><section class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-8\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mb-4\"><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold\">JLPT N5 Kanji Preview</h2><a class=\"text-green-700 font-semibold text-xs md:text-sm\" href=\"/jlpt/n5\">View All →</a></div><div class=\"overflow-x-auto bg-white rounded-2xl border\"><table class=\"w-full\"><thead class=\"bg-slate-100\"><tr><th class=\"px-2 py-2 text-left text-xs md:text-sm\">Kanji</th><th class=\"px-2 py-2 text-left text-xs md:text-sm\">Meaning</th><th class=\"px-2 py-2 text-left text-xs md:text-sm\">Onyomi</th><th class=\"px-2 py-2 text-left text-xs md:text-sm\">Kunyomi</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-t hover:bg-slate-50\"><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium\">日</td><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm\">Sun / Day</td><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm\">ニチ</td><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm\">ひ</td></tr><tr class=\"border-t hover:bg-slate-50\"><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium\">月</td><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm\">Moon / Month</td><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm\">ゲツ</td><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm\">つき</td></tr><tr class=\"border-t hover:bg-slate-50\"><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium\">火</td><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm\">Fire</td><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm\">カ</td><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm\">ひ</td></tr><tr class=\"border-t hover:bg-slate-50\"><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium\">水</td><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm\">Water</td><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm\">スイ</td><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm\">みず</td></tr><tr class=\"border-t hover:bg-slate-50\"><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium\">木</td><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm\">Tree</td><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm\">モク</td><td class=\"px-2 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm\">き</td></tr></tbody></table></div></section><section class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 md:py-12\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6\">Popular Kanji</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 md:gap-5\"><a class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border p-4 md:p-6 text-center hover:shadow-md hover:border-green-300 transition\" href=\"/kanji/love\"><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-2 md:mb-4\">愛</div><div class=\"font-bold text-base md:text-lg\">Love</div><div class=\"text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1\">あい (ai)</div><div class=\"text-[10px] md:text-xs text-green-700 mt-2\">Explore →</div></a><a class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border p-4 md:p-6 text-center hover:shadow-md hover:border-green-300 transition\" href=\"/kanji/god\"><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-2 md:mb-4\">神</div><div class=\"font-bold text-base md:text-lg\">God</div><div class=\"text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1\">かみ (kami)</div><div class=\"text-[10px] md:text-xs text-green-700 mt-2\">Explore →</div></a><a class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border p-4 md:p-6 text-center hover:shadow-md hover:border-green-300 transition\" href=\"/kanji/money\"><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-2 md:mb-4\">金</div><div class=\"font-bold text-base md:text-lg\">Money, Gold</div><div class=\"text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1\">かね (kane)</div><div class=\"text-[10px] md:text-xs text-green-700 mt-2\">Explore →</div></a><a class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border p-4 md:p-6 text-center hover:shadow-md hover:border-green-300 transition\" href=\"/kanji/heart\"><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-2 md:mb-4\">心</div><div class=\"font-bold text-base md:text-lg\">Heart</div><div class=\"text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1\">こころ (kokoro)</div><div class=\"text-[10px] md:text-xs text-green-700 mt-2\">Explore →</div></a></div></section><section class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 md:py-12\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6\">Beginner Guides</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 md:gap-5\"><a class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border p-4 md:p-6 hover:shadow-md hover:border-green-300 transition\" href=\"/guides/introduction-to-japanese-writing\"><div class=\"font-medium\">Introduction To Japanese Writing